To create a JWT token to verify users in a Java server-side and jQuery client-side application, you can follow these steps:

Java Server-side (using Java's JJWT library):

1. Add the JJWT dependencies in your project. If you are using Maven, add this to your `pom.xml`:

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.jsonwebtoken</groupId>
    <artifactId>jjwt-api</artifactId>
    <version>0.11.2</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.jsonwebtoken</groupId>
    <artifactId>jjwt-impl</artifactId>
    <version>0.11.2</version>
    <scope>runtime</scope>
</dependency>
<dependency>
    <groupId>io.jsonwebtoken</groupId>
    <artifactId>jjwt-gson</artifactId>
    <version>0.11.2</version>
    <scope>runtime</scope>
</dependency>
```

2. Create a method for generating a JWT token given the user's information.

```java
import io.jsonwebtoken.Jwts;
import io.jsonwebtoken.SignatureAlgorithm;

import java.security.Key;
import java.util.Date;

public class JwtUtil {
    private static final String SECRET_KEY = "your_secret_key_here"; // Make sure to keep this key secret and secure.

    public static String generateToken(String userId) {
        Date now = new Date();
        Date expiryDate = new Date(now.getTime() + 86400000); // Set expiry date to 86400000 milliseconds (24 hours) later.

        return Jwts.builder()
                .setSubject(userId)
                .setIssuedAt(now)
                .setExpiration(expiryDate)
                .signWith(SignatureAlgorithm.HS512, SECRET_KEY)
                .compact();
    }
}
```

Replace `your_secret_key_here` with your own secret key. Remember to keep this key secret and secure.

3. Create a method to validate the JWT token received from the client-side.

```java
import io.jsonwebtoken.Claims;
import io.jsonwebtoken.Jws;
import io.jsonwebtoken.JwtException;
import io.jsonwebtoken.Jwts;

public class JwtUtil {
    // ...

    public static String parseToken(String token) {
        try {
            Jws<Claims> jws = Jwts.parser().setSigningKey(SECRET_KEY).parseClaimsJws(token);
            return jws.getBody().getSubject(); // Returns the user's ID as the subject
        } catch (JwtException e) {
            return null; // Invalid token
        }
    }
}
```

4. In your server-side logic, after verifying user's credentials (e.g., successful login), generate the JWT token and send it to the client.

```java
String userId = "12345"; // Replace with actual user ID after authentication
String token = JwtUtil.generateToken(userId);

// Send the token to the client-side via your preferred method, e.g., in the response body or as a cookie.
```

Client-side (jQuery):

1. Store the JWT token received from the server. You can choose to store it in a cookie, `localStorage`, or `sessionStorage`.

```javascript
var token = 'your_jwt_token_here'; // Replace with the JWT token received from the server
localStorage.setItem('jwtToken', token);
```

2. When making API requests to your server, include the JWT token as an Authorization header.

```javascript
$.ajax({
  url: 'your_api_endpoint',
  method: 'GET',
  beforeSend: function (xhr) {
    xhr.setRequestHeader('Authorization', 'Bearer ' + localStorage.getItem('jwtToken'));
  },
  success: function (data) {
    console.log('Data:', data);
  },
  error: function (error) {
    console.error('Error:', error);
  },
});
```

Java Server-side (continued):

5. In the server-side, when receiving an API request with the JWT token, validate the token and perform the requested operation. If the token is invalid, return an error response.

```java
String token = "your_jwt_token_here"; // Extract the token from the "Authorization" header from client request
String userId = JwtUtil.parseToken(token);

if (userId == null) {
    // Invalid token. Return an error response.
} else {
    // Valid token. Perform the requested operation.
}
```

In this way, you can create and verify JWT tokens in Java server-side and jQuery client-side applications.

以下是使用JwtSecurityToken生成access token和refresh token的示例代码。在这个示例中，我们使用.NET Core和C#实现。

```csharp
using System;
using System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;
using System.Security.Claims;
using Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;

public class TokenProvider
{
    private readonly string _issuer;
    private readonly string _audience;
    private readonly string _signingKey;
    private readonly int _expiresInMinutes;
    private readonly int _refreshTokenExpiresInDays;

    public TokenProvider(string issuer, string audience, string signingKey, int expiresInMinutes, int refreshTokenExpiresInDays)
    {
        _issuer = issuer;
        _audience = audience;
        _signingKey = signingKey;
        _expiresInMinutes = expiresInMinutes;
        _refreshTokenExpiresInDays = refreshTokenExpiresInDays;
    }

    public string GenerateAccessToken(string userId)
    {
        var claims = new[]{
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Sub, userId),
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Jti, Guid.NewGuid().ToString()),
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Iat, DateTime.UtcNow.ToString())
        };

        var signingKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(_signingKey));
        var signingCredentials = new SigningCredentials(signingKey, SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256);
        var token = new JwtSecurityToken(
            issuer: _issuer,
            audience: _audience,
            claims: claims,
            notBefore: DateTime.UtcNow,
            expires: DateTime.UtcNow.AddMinutes(_expiresInMinutes),
            signingCredentials: signingCredentials
        );
        return new JwtSecurityTokenHandler().WriteToken(token);
    }

    public string GenerateRefreshToken(string userId)
    {
        var claims = new[]{
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Sub, userId),
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Jti, Guid.NewGuid().ToString()),
            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Iat, DateTime.UtcNow.ToString())
        };

        var signingKey = new SymmetricSecurityKey(System.Text.Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(_signingKey));
        var signingCredentials = new SigningCredentials(signingKey, SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256);
        var token = new JwtSecurityToken(
            issuer: _issuer,
            audience: _audience,
            claims: claims,
            notBefore: DateTime.UtcNow,
            expires: DateTime.UtcNow.AddDays(_refreshTokenExpiresInDays),
            signingCredentials: signingCredentials
        );
        return new JwtSecurityTokenHandler().WriteToken(token);
    }
}
```

接下来是如何使用它：

```csharp
var tokenProvider = new TokenProvider(
    issuer: "example.com",
    audience: "example.com",
    signingKey: "a secret used to sign and verify JWT tokens",
    expiresInMinutes: 30,
    refreshTokenExpiresInDays: 30
);

// 生成 access token 和 refresh token
var accessToken = tokenProvider.GenerateAccessToken("user_id");
var refreshToken = tokenProvider.GenerateRefreshToken("user_id");
```

在上面的示例中，我们使用JwtSecurityToken类生成access token和refresh token。在生成token时，我们传递了签名密钥、过期时间和一些其他声明（在这个例子中，这是用户ID）。最后，我们使用JwtSecurityTokenHandler类将JwtSecurityToken对象转换为字符串形式的token。

